<title>HONG KONG: Sterlite launches US$70 mln FRN.</title>
<headline>Sterlite launches US$70 mln FRN.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following issue was announced by lead manager Union Bank of Switzerland.</p>
<p> BORROWER   STERLITE INDUSTRIES (INDIA) LTD</p>
<p> AMOUNT     US$70 MLN  COUPON     6ML+130BP  MATURITY  10 YRS</p>
<p> TYPE	 FRN	  ISS PRICE  PAR	  LAUNCH    08.MAY.97</p>
<p> PUTS	 YR 7	 CALLS	NONE	 REPLIES   20.MAY.97</p>
<p> LISTING    NONE	 REPAYMENT  BULLET     DENOMS    N/A</p>
<p> RATING     NONE	 SALE LMTS  US/UK/HK/SING/INDIA</p>
<p> NEG PLG    YES	  CRS DEF    YES	  FORCE MAJ YES</p>
<p> HOME CTRY  INDIA	GOV LAW    ENGLISH</p>
<p> PAY DATE   30.MAY.97 (TENTATIVELY)</p>
<p> MGT LEVELS AND FEES</p>
<p>   CO-LEAD MANAGERS    US$8 MLN   60BP   ALL-IN  138.57</p>
<p>   CO-MANAGERS	   US$4 MLN   40BP   ALL-IN  135.71</p>
<p> LEAD MANAGER    UNION BANK OF SWITZERLAND</p>
<p> NOTES	     FINANCIAL CONVENANTS</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong newsroom (852) 2843 6960</p>
